 "claims": [],
 "transcript": [
  {
   "start": 0.14,
   "end": 2.88,
   "text": "Or at the archaeological site of Olympus."
  },
  {
   "start": 3.84,
   "end": 4.62,
   "text": "This is it."
  },
  {
   "start": 6.38,
   "end": 8.52,
   "text": "This is where the running foot race is held."
  },
  {
   "start": 9.84,
   "end": 13.44,
   "text": "About 180 meters to 230 meters long."
  },
  {
   "start": 14.44,
   "end": 19.38,
   "text": "And Olympus is also where the lighting of the torch every year has begun."
  },
  {
   "start": 20.42,
   "end": 21.12,
   "text": "And we have water."
  },
  {
   "start": 21.94,
   "end": 22.88,
   "text": "So let's get..."
  },
  {
   "start": 22.88,
   "end": 23.96,
   "text": "We don't have water to drink."
  },
  {
   "start": 24.46,
   "end": 25.36,
   "text": "So let's get going."
  },
  {
   "start": 25.36,
   "end": 30.34,
   "text": "Here we are."
  },
  {
   "start": 31.66,
   "end": 34.98,
   "text": "At the end of the stadium."
  },
  {
   "start": 36.12,
   "end": 39.74,
   "text": "Actually, here, let's walk up the embankment."
  },
  {
   "start": 41.08,
   "end": 45.04,
   "text": "So people would just sit on the grass here and watch."
  },
  {
   "start": 50.28,
   "end": 52.7,
   "text": "It's pretty packed with 45,000 people."
  },
  {
   "start": 53.66,
   "end": 55.3,
   "text": "I think the Coliseum in Rome had 50."
  },
  {
   "start": 55.3,
   "end": 58.6,
   "text": "And Coliseum these days can hold, like maybe."
  },
  {
   "start": 58.6,
   "end": 66.22,
   "text": "And there it is."
  },
  {
   "start": 68.45,
   "end": 70.33,
   "text": "Here's the hill of Conos."
  },
  {
   "start": 71.15,
   "end": 72.45,
   "text": "There's a road that's right there."
  },
  {
   "start": 84.48,
   "end": 89.26,
   "text": "Here's the edge of the Coliseum."
  },
  {
   "start": 90.64,
   "end": 94.82,
   "text": "And so here we are at the Echo Portico Hephaestus."
  },
  {
   "start": 95.04,
   "end": 96.26,
   "text": "Fourth century B.C."
  },
  {
   "start": 96.84,
   "end": 99.5,
   "text": "A sound with echo seven times."
  },
  {
   "start": 99.5,
   "end": 103.66,
   "text": "And so it was the most acoustic and it was right here."
  },
  {
   "start": 103.8,
   "end": 107.18,
   "text": "And they had a statue of Ptolemy."
  },
  {
   "start": 107.36,
   "end": 111.6,
   "text": "I guess one of the ancient Greek kings who I guess paid to have it built."
  },
  {
   "start": 112.4,
   "end": 114.52,
   "text": "And they had some columns 10 meters high."
  },
  {
   "start": 114.74,
   "end": 116.74,
   "text": "These may be the exact columns right here."
  },
  {
   "start": 117.2,
   "end": 119.2,
   "text": "I remember seeing columns like this in the streets of Rome."
  },
  {
   "start": 119.28,
   "end": 119.88,
   "text": "Let's see what's in."
  },
  {
   "start": 120.42,
   "end": 121.38,
   "text": "These are pretty big."
  },
  {
   "start": 121.38,
   "end": 124.02,
   "text": "Let's see how big they are next to my hand."
  },
  {
   "start": 125.22,
   "end": 126.52,
   "text": "So let's see what's this way."
  },
  {
   "start": 127.96,
   "end": 130.76,
   "text": "Here is Nero's."
  },
  {
   "start": 130.76,
   "end": 131.48,
   "text": "What's the wrong one?"
  },
  {
   "start": 131.96,
   "end": 134.1,
   "text": "Here is Nero's house, the octagon."
  },
  {
   "start": 136.48,
   "end": 141.26,
   "text": "Emperor Nero in third century AD came here to participate in the games."
  },
  {
   "start": 141.38,
   "end": 142.26,
   "text": "I think he's a wrestler."
  },
  {
   "start": 142.26,
   "end": 148.36,
   "text": "And so he had, he was a total megalomaniac."
  },
  {
   "start": 149.4,
   "end": 150.86,
   "text": "And I came from this way."
  },
  {
   "start": 152.06,
   "end": 157.08,
   "text": "He had his own, his own like house built so he could live in it while he participated."
  },
  {
   "start": 157.5,
   "end": 171.28,
   "text": "So here's some other ancient, they didn't excavate this until 130 years ago."
  },
  {
   "start": 172.46,
   "end": 174.18,
   "text": "This is as close as I can get."
  },
  {
   "start": 174.18,
   "end": 187.08,
   "text": "But this is the outer part of Nero's palace that he built here to live in while he participated in the games."
  },
  {
   "start": 190.08,
   "end": 194.4,
   "text": "So here's the base of Paeonianus Victory, 5th century BC."
  },
  {
   "start": 195.3,
   "end": 199.1,
   "text": "The Messinians and Malkypians over the Spartans."
  },
  {
   "start": 199.34,
   "end": 203.24,
   "text": "Spartans, we were looking at that in the museum before."
  },
  {
   "start": 203.24,
   "end": 208.42,
   "text": "And it looks like the base still exists."
  },
  {
   "start": 209.54,
   "end": 210.28,
   "text": "Look at that."
  },
  {
   "start": 212.77,
   "end": 214.47,
   "text": "There's Nero's temples right there."
  },
  {
   "start": 215.73,
   "end": 215.93,
   "text": "Hmm."
  },
  {
   "start": 218.46,
   "end": 219.68,
   "text": "Let's go see what's over here."
  },
  {
   "start": 221.42,
   "end": 223.46,
   "text": "The council house, Beliorionion."
  },
  {
   "start": 224.34,
   "end": 228.92,
   "text": "So it's where the Olympic council met and had the big temple of Zeus."
  },
  {
   "start": 230.36,
   "end": 232.02,
   "text": "I think that was 10 meters high."
  },
  {
   "start": 232.18,
   "end": 233.72,
   "text": "The big statue of Zeus, perhaps."
  },
  {
   "start": 233.72,
   "end": 235.68,
   "text": "And they made the O's."
  },
  {
   "start": 235.84,
   "end": 236.98,
   "text": "The athletes made the O's."
  },
  {
   "start": 237.1,
   "end": 237.98,
   "text": "That's what it looked like."
  },
  {
   "start": 239.5,
   "end": 241.4,
   "text": "Here's where it is in the complex."
  },
  {
   "start": 243.79,
   "end": 245.97,
   "text": "So here's what we have."
  },
  {
   "start": 246.03,
   "end": 247.81,
   "text": "I guess we can walk around and look at it."
  },
  {
   "start": 248.75,
   "end": 252.43,
   "text": "Although it's just the base that still existed."
  },
  {
   "start": 252.43,
   "end": 256.81,
   "text": "There's the spire."
  },
  {
   "start": 258.25,
   "end": 260.05,
   "text": "And look at the size of these pillars."
  },
  {
   "start": 260.23,
   "end": 260.77,
   "text": "My God."
  },
  {
   "start": 261.91,
   "end": 262.79,
   "text": "The pillars were huge."
  },
  {
   "start": 262.89,
   "end": 265.29,
   "text": "It's like five, almost six feet tall."
  },
  {
   "start": 266.37,
   "end": 267.17,
   "text": "This side of that pillar."
  },
  {
   "start": 267.83,
   "end": 268.45,
   "text": "Another one."
  },
  {
   "start": 269.27,
   "end": 272.07,
   "text": "Definitely going to see what that big monument is."
  },
  {
   "start": 272.23,
   "end": 272.35,
   "text": "Look."
  },
  {
   "start": 273.63,
   "end": 275.83,
   "text": "It's all just piled on."
  },
  {
   "start": 276.01,
   "end": 277.09,
   "text": "Falling down."
  },
  {
   "start": 279.79,
   "end": 280.13,
   "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
   "start": 280.25,
   "end": 281.05,
   "text": "Let's see what's over here."
  },
  {
   "start": 281.05,
   "end": 288.53,
   "text": "Okay, I came from there."
  },
  {
   "start": 289.37,
   "end": 291.17,
   "text": "You can actually go inside this."
  },
  {
   "start": 293.64,
   "end": 295.38,
   "text": "Inside the temple of Thadius."
  },
  {
   "start": 297.04,
   "end": 298.38,
   "text": "The guy who made it."
  },
  {
   "start": 299.1,
   "end": 300.18,
   "text": "Look at the size of these stones."
  },
  {
   "start": 301.44,
   "end": 302.42,
   "text": "That's really impressive."
  },
  {
   "start": 302.84,
   "end": 306.62,
   "text": "It's nothing compared to Sacsayhuaman and Cusco."
  },
  {
   "start": 306.62,
   "end": 310.72,
   "text": "But it does make you wonder how the hell they move these big old stones around."
  },
  {
   "start": 311.26,
   "end": 315.94,
   "text": "Look, original pillars."
  },
  {
   "start": 315.94,
   "end": 323.89,
   "text": "Just, I think, so far are the biggest."
  },
  {
   "start": 324.99,
   "end": 328.11,
   "text": "You've got kind of a bunch of stuff thrown together."
  },
  {
   "start": 328.23,
   "end": 329.41,
   "text": "Rocks and stone."
  },
  {
   "start": 329.61,
   "end": 330.49,
   "text": "Ivory or whatever."
  },
  {
   "start": 330.89,
   "end": 332.93,
   "text": "Or sandstone or whatever that is."
  },
  {
   "start": 333.93,
   "end": 337.19,
   "text": "And the bricks and the limestone."
  },
  {
   "start": 338.31,
   "end": 338.61,
   "text": "Look."
  },
  {
   "start": 338.71,
   "end": 340.37,
   "text": "Still got some marble down here."
  },
  {
   "start": 340.37,
   "end": 342.43,
   "text": "From back in the day."
  },
  {
   "start": 343.59,
   "end": 344.35,
   "text": "Oh my god."
  },
  {
   "start": 344.41,
   "end": 345.01,
   "text": "And look at this."
  },
  {
   "start": 346.59,
   "end": 348.27,
   "text": "Still have this ornamented."
  },
  {
   "start": 350.01,
   "end": 350.57,
   "text": "Columns."
  },
  {
   "start": 352.48,
   "end": 353.44,
   "text": "And the cross."
  },
  {
   "start": 358.48,
   "end": 360.72,
   "text": "And the columns still standing up over there, too."
  },
  {
   "start": 360.8,
   "end": 361.52,
   "text": "Between the walls."
  },
  {
   "start": 362.8,
   "end": 363.84,
   "text": "They built this quite well."
  },
  {
   "start": 363.98,
   "end": 364.72,
   "text": "It's still standing."
  },
  {
   "start": 365.04,
   "end": 366.06,
   "text": "Thousands of years later."
  },
  {
   "start": 368.26,
   "end": 370.38,
   "text": "Look at the size of that door, too."
  },
  {
   "start": 370.38,
   "end": 372.42,
   "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
   "start": 372.54,
   "end": 374.12,
   "text": "It's big enough for the gods."
  },
  {
   "start": 386.64,
   "end": 387.32,
   "text": "Officials."
  },
  {
   "start": 388.96,
   "end": 389.56,
   "text": "Accommodated."
  },
  {
   "start": 390.06,
   "end": 394.42,
   "text": "It looks like."
  },
  {
   "start": 394.74,
   "end": 398.0,
   "text": "It looks like them."
  },
  {
   "start": 398.52,
   "end": 400.1,
   "text": "They had a water moat around it."
  },
  {
   "start": 402.15,
   "end": 403.61,
   "text": "There's where it is on the site."
  },
  {
   "start": 405.84,
   "end": 406.56,
   "text": "Very large."
  },
  {
   "start": 406.92,
   "end": 407.54,
   "text": "Beneath of it."
  },
  {
   "start": 407.54,
   "end": 419.19,
   "text": "So these."
  },
  {
   "start": 420.19,
   "end": 421.39,
   "text": "This would be inside of it."
  },
  {
   "start": 421.45,
   "end": 422.19,
   "text": "And this row here."
  },
  {
   "start": 423.25,
   "end": 424.51,
   "text": "This would be this row here."
  },
  {
   "start": 425.73,
   "end": 426.97,
   "text": "This would be inside."
  },
  {
   "start": 431.56,
   "end": 434.96,
   "text": "And people's."
  },
  {
   "start": 436.4,
   "end": 438.18,
   "text": "Maybe this is where you'd walk around."
  },
  {
   "start": 438.3,
   "end": 439.86,
   "text": "And then people's rooms would be in here."
  },
  {
   "start": 440.94,
   "end": 442.62,
   "text": "So it's about as big as a normal."
  },
  {
   "start": 443.58,
   "end": 445.04,
   "text": "Nice large room."
  },
  {
   "start": 446.54,
   "end": 448.52,
   "text": "Could be a gigantic hotel room."
  },
  {
   "start": 448.52,
   "end": 449.36,
   "text": "Now a days."
  },
  {
   "start": 450.32,
   "end": 451.38,
   "text": "Well, not gigantic."
  },
  {
   "start": 451.56,
   "end": 452.54,
   "text": "It's average hotel room."
  },
  {
   "start": 454.16,
   "end": 455.58,
   "text": "There's the other room here."
  },
  {
   "start": 458.27,
   "end": 459.71,
   "text": "Really big hallways."
  },
  {
   "start": 460.81,
   "end": 463.19,
   "text": "Much bigger than the hallways we have these days."
  },
  {
   "start": 464.79,
   "end": 467.13,
   "text": "And then you have the rooms around the edges."
  },
  {
   "start": 467.35,
   "end": 469.91,
   "text": "And then closer to the inside."
  },
  {
   "start": 471.21,
   "end": 472.71,
   "text": "You have the other hallway."
  },
  {
   "start": 473.05,
   "end": 474.29,
   "text": "Other lining of hallways."
  },
  {
   "start": 475.45,
   "end": 476.89,
   "text": "And then you have the moat."
  },
  {
   "start": 478.21,
   "end": 479.63,
   "text": "Where the water was."
  },
  {
   "start": 479.95,
   "end": 480.55,
   "text": "Look at that."
  },
  {
   "start": 481.65,
   "end": 483.19,
   "text": "Maybe they swam around and around."
  },
  {
   "start": 483.31,
   "end": 484.63,
   "text": "They should have swimming races in this."
  },
  {
   "start": 485.33,
   "end": 488.07,
   "text": "Must have been just beautiful."
  },
  {
   "start": 490.01,
   "end": 492.85,
   "text": "And then you have an inner moat."
  },
  {
   "start": 494.31,
   "end": 497.29,
   "text": "And then the pretty flowers."
  },
  {
   "start": 498.87,
   "end": 499.27,
   "text": "Everywhere."
  },
  {
   "start": 501.34,
   "end": 502.4,
   "text": "Let's go see what that building is."
  },
  {
   "start": 502.44,
   "end": 504.5,
   "text": "I think that was the hospital where the other people stayed."
  },
  {
   "start": 505.12,
   "end": 507.34,
   "text": "Some kind of thing that looks like an apple that I've been into."
  },
  {
   "start": 507.44,
   "end": 508.76,
   "text": "That's totally bitter and not edible."
  },
  {
   "start": 508.76,
   "end": 511.42,
   "text": "But they're all over these trees."
  },
  {
   "start": 511.54,
   "end": 515.18,
   "text": "I don't know what the heck they are."
  },
  {
   "start": 518.63,
   "end": 520.39,
   "text": "And then the Nodidium Thermi."
  },
  {
   "start": 521.67,
   "end": 523.53,
   "text": "Great and wall heating system."
  },
  {
   "start": 523.97,
   "end": 531.5,
   "text": "Building."
  },
  {
   "start": 531.98,
   "end": 536.64,
   "text": "Some buildings here."
  },
  {
   "start": 538.22,
   "end": 539.58,
   "text": "Heating system's still intact."
  },
  {
   "start": 539.7,
   "end": 543.84,
   "text": "There's a big room building where all the officials lived."
  },
  {
   "start": 543.84,
   "end": 547.08,
   "text": "You can see the central square there."
  },
  {
   "start": 550.06,
   "end": 551.08,
   "text": "Temple of Zeus."
  },
  {
   "start": 552.4,
   "end": 553.04,
   "text": "Over there."
  },
  {
   "start": 553.12,
   "end": 559.74,
   "text": "And there's the hill of the other god in front of us."
  },
  {
   "start": 559.9,
   "end": 567.36,
   "text": "So intact."
  },
  {
   "start": 567.68,
   "end": 577.9,
   "text": "Those on the bottom."
  },
  {
   "start": 578.98,
   "end": 580.58,
   "text": "Different kinds of stonework."
  },
  {
   "start": 580.84,
   "end": 583.82,
   "text": "Just together."
  },
  {
   "start": 584.34,
   "end": 591.31,
   "text": "All the truth."
  },
  {
   "start": 595.52,
   "end": 595.82,
   "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
   "start": 595.82,
   "end": 598.46,
   "text": "It's still together after so many thousands of years."
  },
  {
   "start": 598.72,
   "end": 599.92,
   "text": "It's nice and cool in here too."
  },
  {
   "start": 606.38,
   "end": 607.1,
   "text": "Let's see what's over here."
  },
  {
   "start": 607.1,
   "end": 617.92,
   "text": "This building is made of glass manufacturing place in the 5th and 6th centuries AD."
  },
  {
   "start": 618.14,
   "end": 619.82,
   "text": "So maybe this is what this building is here."
  },
  {
   "start": 619.96,
   "end": 621.74,
   "text": "But I'm going to sit down."
  }
 ]
}